729683f-a.title: Richmond: Sprague Avenue - Surf Avenue
729683f-a.text:
Sprague Avenue, east side, between Surf Avenue
and Clermont Avenue. This house was owned by Captain
Nartin in 1874; by James Steel in 1898: )y Catherine
McDonald in 1907, and by the Rully Realty Co. in 1917.
August 8, 1936
P. L. Sperr
NO RECRODUCTIONS
